{"tid":1476944,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 PS5 明年 2 月發佈　效能達 RTX 2080 級數","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T03:38:46.000Z","uid":187876,"like":12,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9a75bb653e1b225784040f87ae6c32d48cdc12","tid":1476944,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"早前為各位報導過，微軟新一代遊戲主機，將會著重遊戲的流暢度及載入速度，不過作為主要對手的 Sony PlayStation ，現在又再有新傳聞出現，就是關於 PlayStation 5 將會在明年的 2 月 12 日發佈，並有更多硬件上的資料流出，現在一同看看吧。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Sony 將會在明年的 2 月 12 日的PlayStation大會上發佈次世代主機 PlayStation 5 ，爆料人Komachi透露，PS5所用GPU頻率達到2GHz，浮點性能9.2TB，足足是Xbox One X的2.3倍，相當於桌面電腦的 RTX 2080 顯示卡效能。<br />\n<br />\n配合已經公佈的硬件資料來看，PS5採用Zen 2架構CPU、navi GPU，支援即時光影追蹤，及8K輸出、4K 120Hz遊戲，要有RTX 2080 顯示卡的效能絕對是需要的，而各位都知道，家用遊戲主機的軟硬件，全是為遊戲而設，穩定度、表現都會比同級 PC 更好。<br />\n<br />\n目前尚未知道消息是否屬實，但按照 Sony PlayStation 4 在2013年2月20日發佈，年底發售，因此可以推測，我們可以在 2020 年底購買到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/08/15/ps5-launch-date-rumors/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2Fps5-launch-date-rumors%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d54fba19\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/08/15/ps5-launch-date-rumors/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"95c40cefa2481ffad649f44d384b565dd2613a8c","tid":1476944,"uid":46064,"like":19,"dislike":56,"score":-37,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"又4K又8K吹到咁大<br />\n講真你做到畫質提升+1080p+60fps就夠<br />\n屋企撚有位擺4K電視咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77080e9f687d6d02a2d5726debe9255501b9019f","tid":1476944,"uid":56649,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"95c40cefa2481ffad649f44d384b565dd2613a8c","tid":1476944,"uid":46064,"like":19,"dislike":56,"score":-37,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"又4K又8K吹到咁大<br />\n講真你做到畫質提升+1080p+60fps就夠<br />\n屋企撚有位擺4K電視咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji